    <item>
      <title>美元秋千将创意日元公牛驱动到欧洲的行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/dollar-swings-drive-creative-yen-bulls-to-european-based-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者在押注主要经济体的利率方面的赌注方向上发挥创造力，因为他们寻找避开美元波动率的方法，而是利用欧洲货币来资助日元日元的赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/dollar-swings-drive-creative-yen-bulls-to-european-based-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 22:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元往返的兴起为亚洲中央银行带来风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/rise-of-dollar-forwards-builds-risk-for-asia-s-central-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲的中央银行越来越多地利用衍生品来保护其货币免受强大的美元侵害，提出了有关他们可以这样做的时间以及他们是否只是在为未来储备麻烦的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/rise-of-dollar-forwards-builds-risk-for-asia-s-central-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
